text: Eupsilobiidae is a family of beetles in the order Coleoptera, formerly included within the family Endomychidae. There are at least two genera and three described species in Eupsilobiidae. ==Genera== * Eidoreus Sharp, 1885 * Evolocera Sharp, 1902 ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * * * * * * * * Category:Coccinelloidea Category:Polyphaga families
